DESCRIPTION:What makes a community truly exceptional? The people who lead w
	ith heart\, serve with purpose\, and make a lasting impact every single da
	y. Join us for one of the most meaningful events of the year - the 90th An
	nual Kirkland Chamber Award's Luncheon - where we honor the individuals\, 
	businesses\, and organizations whose dedication helps our community thrive
	. Event Details: Date: Friday\, February 13th Time: 11:30 AM - 1:30 PM \\(
	doors open at 11 AM for networking\\) Ticket Cost: $65 members\, $89 non-m
	embers. Lunch is included. This inspiring afternoon brings together leader
	s\, changemakers\, and neighbors to recognize excellence across even signa
	ture awards. Every honoree reflects the spirit of Kirkland: connection\, s
	ervice\, generosity\, and innovation. From visionary business leaders who 
	innovate and raise the bar to dedicated volunteers who never ask for credi
	t\, to passionate artists who bring the city to life\, and generous philan
	thropists\, this is our moment to celebrate them. ﻿﻿Be part of an upliftin
	g afternoon that reminds us what community is all about. This event has be
	en brought to you by: EvergreenHealth\, Gesa Credit Union\, Kirkland Commu
	nity Foundation\, Lee Johnson Auto Group\, Plymouth Housing\, and Port of 
	Seattle
